reuters.title: AIR WIS <ARWS> FEBRUARY LOAD FACTOR FALLS
reuters.body: Air Wis Services Inc said February load factor fell to 42.9 pct from 44.2 pct a year before. The company said revenue passenger miles rose 2.1 pct to 22.2 mln from 21.7 mln a year before, with available seat miles up 5.3 pct to 51.8 mln from 49.2 mln. Reuter 
